Class SimpleRegressionAnalysis

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.reporting.destination.anomalyDetection.SimpleRegressionAnalysis

  • public class SimpleRegressionAnalysis
extends Object
    Implementation of simple regression analysis for detecting anomalies in data set. Degradation of some metrics or regular spikes can be identified.

    Martina Kůrová
